{"tid":914464,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我搭上咗個想畀人姦嘅痴女［甜故］［重新修訂版］","createTime":"2018-11-24T10:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:48:57.000Z","uid":199586,"like":68,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4e99029de2b40d7713fa4597ae01b233cc06f2","tid":914464,"uid":199586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"以下有幾樣嘢我想講，請大家耐心睇晒。<br />\n首先，對於先前因為私事而消失一事深表歉意，望各位巴絲可以不計前嫌，繼續支持小弟。<br />\n其次，基於我發現故入面嘅錯字以及謬誤都幾多，所以將會將劇情增加以及重新校對，由頭再寫一次，希望可以提供一個更加優質嘅故畀大家。<br />\n同時，我已經冇用TG，因為我發現我自己時間分配都唔夠平均，希望大家體諒，所以更新時間都唔會再係一日兩更，而係隨時間而更新，不過我會盡量更新多啲。<br />\n最後，希望大家可以繼續支持我，我將會重新開post，於下星期五開始更新。"},{"pid":"6f745b27ee27518b618ce7cb9b74676655bde72d","tid":914464,"uid":135381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:11:39.000Z","msg":"即刻正皮支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43fc0302bae42f3955c2d35c34956245f1da432","tid":914464,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c511109b0996cb6a1a50d6fad62e5bcbebf1e30","tid":914464,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 唔好玩穿越同超能力得唔得"},{"pid":"0e02cc0c143e3479c2d29b1d5f20a140e637d21a","tid":914464,"uid":98502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:16:42.000Z","msg":"先留名"},{"pid":"eb815b656d9fa031b9524e18c9ff319cf3df6b75","tid":914464,"uid":66044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"正皮支持"},{"pid":"70fc23f2f4bf49e3647a3f1268688c8f28bd1dbc","tid":914464,"uid":198455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr